type Group : Monoid as G

    + axiom
        + inverse : forall x : G ,
                    exist  x_inv : G ,
                    op x x_inv = id , op x_inv x = id

    + desc
        A group amo::''G'' is a monoid with an additional axiom stipulating
        that any element amo::''x'' admits an inverse amo::''x_inv'' verifying
        amo::''G.op x x_inv = G.id'' and amo::''G.op x_inv x = G.id''.
